    • Method Detail

      • parseSamples

        public void parseSamples()
                  throws Exception
        Parse all Kraken2Classifier reports in the input directory.
        Build an Kraken2Node for each line.
        If ParserModuleImpl.isValid(OtuNode),
        1. Create ParsedSample for the OtuNodeImpl.getSampleId() if not yet created.
        2. Add the OtuNodeImpl.getCount() (1) to ParsedSample OTU count.

        Sample Kraken report line (head 7A_1_reported.tsv) :
        d__Bacteria|p__Bacteroidetes|c__Bacteroidia|o__Bacteroidales 20094

        Specified by:
        parseSamples in interface ParserModule
        Specified by:
        parseSamples in class ParserModuleImpl
        Throws:
        Exception - if error occurs while parsing classifier reports
